OL,6,FThe average annual council tax bill
OL,7,Fwill rise by #106 this year as local
OL,8,Fauthorities seek to maximise revenue
OL,9,Fto pay for struggling frontline
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,FThe bill for an average Band D
OL,13,Fproperty will increase by 5% to
